<p itemprop="description">The head of IT service management provides strategic leadership for all service management activities across the organisation. They establish enterprise-wide service management frameworks and ensure services consistently deliver business value.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide strategic leadership for service management across the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish enterprise-wide service management frameworks and governance</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive service-oriented digital transformation initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead service portfolio strategy and investment planning</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent service management interests in executive forums</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure alignment between service strategy and business objectives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop strategic partnerships with service providers and vendors</li>
    </ul>
</section>

